org.corfudb.runtime.object

Class AbstractCorfuWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.corfudb.runtime.object.AbstractCorfuWrapper<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICorfuSMRProxyWrapper<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FGMap

    public abstract class AbstractCorfuWrapper<T>
extends Object
implements ICorfuSMRProxyWrapper<T>
    A Corfu container object is a container for other Corfu objects. It has explicit access to its own stream ID, and a runtime, allowing it to manipulate and return other Corfu objects.

    Created by mwei on 11/12/16.
